it's really easy

00:23:39.050 --> 00:23:46.424
to get lost in security
and a groove and a rut.

00:23:46.424 --> 00:23:48.590
And the only difference
between a groove and a grave

00:23:48.590 --> 00:23:51.980
is a couple of feet, so you
have to be careful about that.

00:23:51.980 --> 00:23:56.620
And being willing to face
your fears of embarrassment,

00:23:56.620 --> 00:24:00.140
failure, rejection.

