Now I had a new problem.

00:26:12.400 --> 00:26:15.760
I needed three more rejections
or I couldn't go to Hawaii.

00:26:15.760 --> 00:26:17.670
So I figured I'd start
acting like a jerk.

00:26:17.670 --> 00:26:25.370
So I go up to a woman,
I go hey sugar lips.

