I was just crying.

00:52:42.200 --> 00:52:43.210
I just kept crying.

00:52:43.210 --> 00:52:44.790
I couldn't stop crying.

00:52:44.790 --> 00:52:48.540
I had never felt so
much love in my life.

00:52:48.540 --> 00:52:50.830
And I'm sitting
there practically

00:52:50.830 --> 00:52:52.610
drooling in his lap crying.

00:52:52.610 --> 00:52:58.430
And as I'm in his lap crying,
he taps me on the head

00:52:58.430 --> 00:53:00.170
and he said something
I'll never forget.

00:53:00.170 --> 00:53:06.530
He says, this love you're
feeling now is who you are.

00:53:06.530 --> 00:53:12.710
This joy you're feeling now is
who you are in your essence.

00:53:12.710 --> 00:53:18.071
And your job in this world
is to never forget that.

00:53:20.780 --> 00:53:27.800
So that has stayed with me,
and I echo his words to you.

00:53:27.800 --> 00:53:37.640
Love is who we are, and your
job is to get in touch with that

00:53:37.640 --> 00:53:40.920
because only if you get in
touch with some peace and love

00:53:40.920 --> 00:53:43.590
and happiness can
you really give

00:53:43.590 --> 00:53:46.880
your best to a world
in desperate need,

00:53:46.880 --> 00:53:51.771
and really give your best to
the people you most care about.

00:53:51.771 --> 00:53:53.270
Thank you for
listening to me today.

00:53:53.270 --> 00:53:53.770
Thank you.

