00:55:01.580 --> 00:55:02.970
That is a lifelong question.

00:55:02.970 --> 00:55:06.550
It's like a friend, and
it keeps on-- as I ask it,

00:55:06.550 --> 00:55:09.790
I keep on getting to deeper and
deeper, more subtle and subtle

00:55:09.790 --> 00:55:11.530
levels of that question.

00:55:11.530 --> 00:55:13.780
Or how can I know
gratitude more?

00:55:13.780 --> 00:55:16.600
Just keep that question
alive in your life.

