00:55:52.360 --> 00:55:53.820
I'm pretty good most the time.

00:55:53.820 --> 00:55:55.445
There's going to be
some ups and downs.

00:55:55.445 --> 00:55:57.030
Do you look at it like that?

00:55:57.030 --> 00:55:58.200
Or is there maybe--

00:55:58.200 --> 00:56:00.200
JONATHAN ROBINSON: Yeah,
I look at it like that.

00:56:00.200 --> 00:56:02.206
And everybody, no matter
how happy they are,

00:56:02.206 --> 00:56:04.230
they have good
moments, bad moments.

00:56:04.230 --> 00:56:06.910
Every now and then, you'll
find yourself in a good moment.

00:56:06.910 --> 00:56:09.030
That happens, right?

00:56:09.030 --> 00:56:11.380
Give it some more space.

00:56:11.380 --> 00:56:14.140
A lot of times, you're
happy-- the other day,

00:56:14.140 --> 00:56:15.960
I was enjoying my dog.

00:56:15.960 --> 00:56:18.250
I was petting her, telling
her how much I love her.

00:56:18.250 --> 00:56:20.250
And then I thought, oh,
I got stuff to do today.

00:56:20.250 --> 00:56:22.374
And I said, what could be
more important than this?

00:56:22.374 --> 00:56:23.350
I'm loving this.

00:56:23.350 --> 00:56:24.280
My dog's loving it.

00:56:24.280 --> 00:56:26.363
I'm just going to sit here
and keep on telling her

00:56:26.363 --> 00:56:29.320
how much I love her until I
don't want to do that anymore.

00:56:29.320 --> 00:56:33.800
We don't even give our happy,
joyful, intimate moments space.

00:56:33.800 --> 00:56:35.990
We're always moving
on to the next thing.

00:56:35.990 --> 00:56:40.230
So one way to be happier is
just to take the happy moments

00:56:40.230 --> 00:56:43.390
you have and don't go onto
the next thing so quickly.

00:56:43.390 --> 00:56:45.770
But yeah, wherever
your life is, you're

00:56:45.770 --> 00:56:48.370
going to have ups and downs.

00:56:48.370 --> 00:56:52.770
But over time, you learn to
let go of the negative emotions

00:56:52.770 --> 00:56:53.715
more quickly.

00:56:53.715 --> 00:56:54.590
Think of little kids.

00:56:54.590 --> 00:56:56.660
They let go of negative
emotions like that.

00:56:56.660 --> 00:56:58.870
They can go from
totally having a tantrum

00:56:58.870 --> 00:57:01.890
to fine in two minutes.

00:57:01.890 --> 00:57:04.680
Some adults, they have
a problem with somebody,

00:57:04.680 --> 00:57:07.660
they don't let go for years.

00:57:07.660 --> 00:57:10.070
So you learn to let go of the
negative emotions quickly.

00:57:10.070 --> 00:57:11.690
You give the positive
emotions more space.

00:57:11.690 --> 00:57:13.148
And soon, you'll
find that you just

00:57:13.148 --> 00:57:15.080
feel better a lot
more of the time.

